; 
<bibRefCitation author="FOHRER B. &amp; NEMYROVSKA T. I. &amp; SAMANKASSOU E. &amp; UENO K." box="[951,1157,1650,1676]" pageId="19" pageNumber="544" pagination="1 - 85" refId="ref22065" refString="FOHRER B., NEMYROVSKA T. I., SAMANKASSOU E. &amp; UENO K. 2007. - The Pennsylvanian (Moscovian) Izvarino section, Donets Basin, Ukraine: a multidisciplinary study on microfa- cies, biostratigraphy (conodonts, foraminifers, and ostracodes), and paleoecology. Journal of Paleontology 81 (69): 1 - 85. https: // doi. org / 10.1666 / 06 - 121.1" type="journal article" year="2007">
